archimate:DataObject.name: UsageVolumeBalanceDebit
archimate:DataObject.documentation: The UsageVolumeBalanceDebit represents an amount in a certain unit that decrements the UsageVolumeBalance. The UsageVolumeBalanceDebit is the result of applying a particular UsageVolumeChargingRule for a ProductUsage and decrements the balance of the UsageVolumeProduct (UsageVolumeBalance).
